  "description": "Sheng with maximum chiff transient and the fastest possible attack. Each note arrives as a 15ms burst of noise-pitched energy before settling into the harmonic series — the Sheng's characteristic 'air rush' on initial breath. At fast playing speeds the chiff overlaps, creating a percussive texture underneath the melody. The breath visible in the sound.",
